# Todo List

Initial MVP of a todo app built with Vite and vanilla JavaScript.

## Features
- Add a new todo
- Mark a todo as complete/incomplete
- Delete a todo
- Persist todos in browser `localStorage`
- Show empty state when there are no todos

## Tech
- Vite
- Vanilla JavaScript
- No backend (browser-only prototype)

## Run locally
1. Install dependencies: `npm install`
2. Start the dev server: `npm run dev`
3. Open the local URL shown in the terminal

## Build for production
- Run `npm run build`

## Quick manual test checklist
- Add two todos and confirm both appear
- Toggle one todo completed and refresh the page
- Confirm completion state is still persisted after refresh
- Delete one todo and confirm it is removed
- Delete all todos and confirm the empty-state message appears
